description: Recently sold: $324,900. Private 1 ?? acre treed lot with potential for horses! description:
Recently sold: $214,400. Priced to sell! Charming and very unique! 3 Bedroom, 1 Bath Ranch/Carriage style house on .45 acres with courtyard and super-sized finished garage. Room for additional half bath in basement. 1,356 finished sq feet + 816 sq ft. finished, heated, dry-walled garage with all new cement floor and lots of overhead lighting, ceiling fans and electrical outlets. Located between Farmington and Northfield, home is close to the cities but just enough into the country to give you that fresh country air. Beautiful tree in center of courtyard with outside patio and adjoining flagstone fire pit makes this home fantastic for outside entertaining. Remodeled kitchen with new lighting, subway tiles and more. Master bedroom adjoins bathroom with walk-through closet with built-in wardrobe and dresser. 3rd bedroom has separate outside entry- nice for home office, Mother in law or older child. Remodeled bath with new tile on floor and walls, new vanity, lighting and more.
This remodel offers a little modern and a little old style-maintaining the craftsmanship and beauty of the original interior door frames, woodwork and hardwood flooring. Architectural shingled new roofs on both structures approx. 4 years ago. Also, a new structural roof gable and main door porch overhang and column was added. Totally new cement in garage and outside also approx 4 years ago. Mostly original wood floors and some new wood laminate flooring. New lighting and ceiling fans. Very clean, fresh dry basement. Room to park up to 6 cars plus boat or RV. 
Landscaped open yard includes Jack pines, Birch and Black Walnut trees. Flower bed and plenty of space for your garden. Also features a shed with cement foundation and fenced dog run or chicken coop. Home has its own well and septic which have all been inspected and in compliance. Washer, dryer, dishwasher, refrigerator and some additional furnishings ALL convey. Home is all freshly painted throughout -SUPER CLEAN and move-in-ready. Pre-qualified buyers only please. Closing must be within 30 days.
(2.7% commission paid to selling broker/agent)
